# Data Model for Workflow Simulation

The next phase of the project will simulate TM operations using the following tables:

## alerts

Stores alerts generated by detection rules.

Fields:

* alert_id
* rule_name
* customer_id
* alert_date
* risk_score
* alert_status

---

## cases

Stores investigation cases.

Fields:

* case_id
* alert_id
* investigator_name
* case_status
* disposition
* case_open_date
* case_close_date

---

## case_notes

Stores investigator observations.

Fields:

* note_id
* case_id
* note_date
* investigator_notes

---

